sh_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "720x1280", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 10220341, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.101 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 880.969, "format": "dash-886783563847281v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}, {"format_id": "dash-923535270244849v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1282.781, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQPS6xDx8ibopMWE7aIDWnM5nHPwika2skKnXpVFa7nEpsowT63jEYw1gHVT9Wsir5-hVv2O5wLoVrjxSLOVxsfKbUVoD0k1m_dEuw3iuwEoOA.mp4?_nc_cat=106&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=Wgb1XeLM5fQQ7kNvwFcbldK&%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=W4k4ki3t0P75ZBLFB5lfBQ&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af11mbhvi1wlRJ2KHEpo0UfRbxxyW9V6ypnWE3inafpnFw&oe=69DE0C0A", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 14881863, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.101 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1282.781, "format": "dash-923535270244849v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by very.kat", "description": "If these insights resonate with you, let’s connect! I explore somatic healing, emotional clarity and spiritual side of everyday life ❤️\n\n#somatic #nervoussystemhealing #listentoyourbody #mindfulness #mindfulmoments #mindfullife #nervoussystemregulation #consciousness #quantumphysics #neuroscience #spirituality #spirituallife", "duration": 92.81, "timestamp": 1768631323, "uploader_id": "61348510818", "uploader": "Kate ☀️", "channel": "very.kat", "like_count": 1983, "comment_count": 71, "comments": [{"author": "bophish", "author_id": "2107636233", "id": "17898812658424124", "text": "🤯", "timestamp": 1775646877}, {"author": "kevinmurphy_author", "author_id": "237870257", "id": "17978834135996320", "text": "if people believe the end is near  they bring the end closer.", "timestamp": 1774961734}, {"author": "aleabarry", "author_id": "1672649815", "id": "18068154953654338", "text": "this is fascinating! it's essentially an explanation of confirmation bias and self-fulfilling prophecy but through the lens of quantum physics, and you articulated it very well. so cool!", "timestamp": 1774922822}, {"author": "applta", "author_id": "61728526524", "id": "18100417417970757", "text": "You are a very interesting woman.", "timestamp": 1774916318}, {"author": "antoinevandewoude", "author_id": "1735252038", "id": "18100179047055852", "text": "❤️", "timestamp": 1774868418}, {"author": "cgnschuec", "author_id": "4175457829", "id": "17955395382088339", "text": "Yes! ❤️🙌🔥👏 \n\nEven time is just an illusion. Ego doesn’t exist, etc. We created this via meta-cognition as a survival instinct. \n\nThe part of info actually taken in from the outside is minimal for most situations / people. \n\nThanks. Following. 🙌", "timestamp": 1774197759}, {"author": "gvangeyte", "author_id": "5524177793", "id": "18384477259086392", "text": "What got you to think about this? I agree", "timestamp": 1773971078}, {"author": "mostevens368", "author_id": "8296807387", "id": "17914612167149704", "text": "I do somatics work with folks and would love to connect and build relationship! Dm if it feels amplifying!", "timestamp": 1773930536}, {"author": "1legendinthesea", "author_id": "61633282921", "id": "18088481474229182", "text": "🔥 Your brain doesn’t create reality—God does.\nScience describes fragments; Scripture reveals the whole truth. \nThe idea that consciousness \"samples reality\" based on expectation sounds profound—but it replaces the Creator with a system. The Bible says: \"The Lord knoweth the thoughts of man, that they are vanity\" (Psalm 94:11 KJV).\nYou are not a quantum observer collapsing reality by prediction. You are a living soul, formed by God: \"And the Lord God formed man of the dust of the ground, and breathed into his nostrils the breath of life; and man became a living soul.\" — Genesis 2:7 KJV\nYour sense of self isn’t reconstructed each moment. It is established in creation and redeemed by Christ. Reality isn’t shaped by your brain’s expectations—it is upheld by His word: \"Upholding all things by the word of his power\" — Hebrews 1:3 KJV\nYour mind is not a prediction engine. It must be renewed by the Spirit: \"Be not conformed to this world: but be ye transformed by the renewing of your mind\" — Romans 12:2 KJV\nAnd salvation? Not a mental projection. It’s a finished work: \"For by grace are ye saved through faith; and that not of yourselves: it is the gift of God\" — Ephesians 2:8 KJV\n👉 Repent of your unbelief \n👉 Believe in the Lord Jesus Christ—His death, burial, and resurrection.\n👉 Call on His name and be saved.\nNow is the day of salvation — not by your measurement, but by His mercy.", "timestamp": 1773900275}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/617770264_658218113984120_5280302385564914310_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGPVXMvB3wwiy-A5VQw4AqM3JxZXlGFH-VUcFm5goAjISmtH5VbhWagawJfbI38S7Q&_nc_ohc=x09qtQgAQtkQ7kNvwHS6Kpc&_nc_gid=W4k4ki3t0P7